&lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot; style=&quot;margin-left:-0.1000pt;mso-para-margin-left:-0.0100gd;text-indent:21.0000pt;
mso-char-indent-count:2.0000;line-height:20.0000pt;mso-line-height-rule:exactly;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;font-size:10.5000pt;
mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;&quot;&gt;中国工商银行股份有限公司湖南省分行现就&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;font-size:10.5000pt;
mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;&quot;&gt;湖南分行全员阅读悦课项目&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;font-size:10.5000pt;
mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;&quot;&gt;进行招标采购。&lt;/span&gt;&lt;b&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;mso-ansi-font-weight:bold;
font-size:10.5000pt;mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;&quot;&gt;&lt;o:p&gt;&lt;/o:p&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/b&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot; style=&quot;text-indent:21.1000pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0000;line-height:20.0000pt;
mso-line-height-rule:exactly;&quot;&gt;&lt;b&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: 宋体; font-size: 10.5pt;&quot;&gt;一、项目名称及招标编号：&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/b&gt;&lt;b&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: 宋体; font-size: 10.5pt;&quot;&gt;&lt;o:p&gt;&lt;/o:p&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/b&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot; style=&quot;text-indent:21.0000pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0000;line-height:20.0000pt;
mso-line-height-rule:exactly;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;font-size:10.5000pt;
mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;&quot;&gt;1.项目名称：&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;font-size:10.5000pt;
mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;&quot;&gt;湖南分行全员阅读悦课项目&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;font-size:10.5000pt;
mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;&quot;&gt;&lt;o:p&gt;&lt;/o:p&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot; style=&quot;text-indent:21.0000pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0000;line-height:20.0000pt;
mso-line-height-rule:exactly;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;font-size:10.5000pt;
mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;&quot;&gt;2.招标编号：&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;font-size:10.5000pt;
mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;&quot;&gt;ZKGS(ZB)-20260372&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;font-size:12.0000pt;
mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;&quot;&gt;&lt;o:p&gt;&lt;/o:p&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot; style=&quot;text-indent:21.1000pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0000;line-height:20.0000pt;
mso-line-height-rule:exactly;&quot;&gt;&lt;b&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: 宋体; font-size: 10.5pt;&quot;&gt;二、项目简介&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/b&gt;&lt;b&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: 宋体; font-size: 10.5pt;&quot;&gt;&lt;o:p&gt;&lt;/o:p&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/b&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot; style=&quot;text-indent:21.0000pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0000;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;
mso-pagination:none;line-height:150%;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;mso-hansi-font-family:'Times New Roman';
font-size:10.5000pt;mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;&quot;&gt;1.采购内&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;mso-hansi-font-family:'Times New Roman';
font-size:10.5000pt;mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;&quot;&gt;容：&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;font-size:10.5000pt;
mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;&quot;&gt;&lt;font face=&quot;宋体&quot;&gt;本次&lt;/font&gt;&lt;font face=&quot;宋体&quot;&gt;&ldquo;全员阅读&rdquo;项目主要为全行员工提供荐书、购书（&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;font-size:10.5000pt;
mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;&quot;&gt;不限于纸&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;font-size:10.5000pt;
mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;&quot;&gt;质&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;font-size:10.5000pt;
mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;&quot;&gt;书、电子书、有声书&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;font-size:10.5000pt;
mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;&quot;&gt;、知识付费会员、文创产品&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;font-size:10.5000pt;
mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;&quot;&gt;等&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;font-size:10.5000pt;
mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;&quot;&gt;）、享书的多渠道学习服务，通过&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;font-size:10.5000pt;
mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;&quot;&gt;对本行员工进行购买额度授权，&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;font-size:10.5000pt;
mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;&quot;&gt;员工可&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;font-size:10.5000pt;
mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;&quot;&gt;在额度范围内进行购书交易&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;font-size:10.5000pt;
mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;&quot;&gt;，并享受全方位的&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;font-size:10.5000pt;
mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;&quot;&gt;售后服务&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;font-size:10.5000pt;
mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;&quot;&gt;&lt;font face=&quot;宋体&quot;&gt;。采购结果适用范围是中国工商银行湖南省分行辖属各级机构。详见《第四章&lt;/font&gt; &amp;nbsp;&lt;font face=&quot;宋体&quot;&gt;技术要求与服务内容》&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;font-size:10.5000pt;
mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;&quot;&gt;&lt;o:p&gt;&lt;/o:p&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p class=&quot;MsoBodyText2&quot; style=&quot;line-height:20.0000pt;mso-line-height-rule:exactly;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;font-size:10.5000pt;
mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&lt;font face=&quot;宋体&quot;&gt;2.&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;font-size:10.5000pt;
mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;&quot;&gt;服务周期&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;font-size:10.5000pt;
mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;&quot;&gt;：&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;font-size:10.5000pt;
mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;&quot;&gt;3&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;font-size:10.5000pt;
mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;&quot;&gt;年&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;font-size:10.5000pt;
mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;&quot;&gt;。&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;font-size:10.5000pt;
mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;&quot;&gt;&lt;o:p&gt;&lt;/o:p&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p class=&quot;MsoBodyText2&quot; style=&quot;text-indent:21.0000pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0000;line-height:20.0000pt;
mso-line-height-rule:exactly;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;font-size:10.5000pt;
mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;&quot;&gt;3.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;font-size:10.5000pt;
mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;&quot;&gt;入选供应商&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;font-size:10.5000pt;
mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;&quot;&gt;数量：&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;font-size:10.5000pt;
mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;&quot;&gt;2家&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;font-size:10.5000pt;
mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;&quot;&gt;。&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;font-size:10.5000pt;
mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;&quot;&gt;&lt;o:p&gt;&lt;/o:p&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot; style=&quot;text-indent:21.0000pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0000;line-height:20.0000pt;
mso-line-height-rule:exactly;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;font-size:10.5000pt;
mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;&quot;&gt;4.资金来源：企业自筹。&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;font-size:10.5000pt;
mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;&quot;&gt;&lt;o:p&gt;&lt;/o:p&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot; style=&quot;text-indent:21.0000pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0000;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;
mso-pagination:none;line-height:150%;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;font-size:10.5000pt;
mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;&quot;&gt;5.金额估算：&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;font-size:10.5000pt;
mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;&quot;&gt;1800万元&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;font-size:10.5000pt;
mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;&quot;&gt;。&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;font-size:10.5000pt;
mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;&quot;&gt;&lt;o:p&gt;&lt;/o:p&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot; style=&quot;text-indent:21.1000pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0000;line-height:20.0000pt;
mso-line-height-rule:exactly;&quot;&gt;&lt;b&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: 宋体; font-size: 10.5pt;&quot;&gt;三、合格投标人的基本资质要求：&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/b&gt;&lt;b&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: 宋体; font-size: 10.5pt;&quot;&gt;&lt;o:p&gt;&lt;/o:p&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/b&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p class=&quot;MsoBodyText2&quot; style=&quot;text-indent:21.0000pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0000;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;
mso-pagination:none;line-height:150%;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;font-size:10.5000pt;
mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;&quot;&gt;1.投标人具有独立承担民事责任的能力，依法取得企业营业执照，营业执照处于有效期。&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;font-size:10.5000pt;
mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;&quot;&gt;&lt;o:p&gt;&lt;/o:p&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p class=&quot;MsoBodyText2&quot; style=&quot;text-indent:21.0000pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0000;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;
mso-pagination:none;line-height:150%;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;font-size:10.5000pt;
mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;&quot;&gt;2.截至投标截止日,投标人未被&ldquo;信用中国&rdquo;网站列入失信被执行人、重大税收违法失信主体、政府采购严重违法失信行为记录名单(提供查询记录截屏)。&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;font-size:10.5000pt;
mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;&quot;&gt;&lt;o:p&gt;&lt;/o:p&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p class=&quot;MsoBodyText2&quot; style=&quot;text-indent:21.0000pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0000;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;
mso-pagination:none;line-height:150%;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;font-size:10.5000pt;
mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;&quot;&gt;3.未列入中国工商银行供应商禁入名单和负面清单(提供书面承诺)。&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;font-size:10.5000pt;
mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;&quot;&gt;&lt;o:p&gt;&lt;/o:p&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p class=&quot;MsoBodyText2&quot; style=&quot;text-indent:21.0000pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0000;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;
mso-pagination:none;line-height:150%;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;font-size:10.5000pt;
mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;&quot;&gt;4.投标人不得直接或间接地与招标人为本项目所委托的咨询公司或其附属机构有任何关联。&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;font-size:10.5000pt;
mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;&quot;&gt;&lt;o:p&gt;&lt;/o:p&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p class=&quot;MsoBodyText2&quot; style=&quot;text-indent:21.0000pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0000;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;
mso-pagination:none;line-height:150%;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;font-size:10.5000pt;
mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;&quot;&gt;5.投标人法定代表人、控股股东或实际控制人与招标人高管人员及使用需求部门、采购部门关键岗位人员无夫妻、直系血亲、三代以内旁系血亲或者近姻亲关系(提供书面承诺)。&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;font-size:10.5000pt;
mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;&quot;&gt;&lt;o:p&gt;&lt;/o:p&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p class=&quot;MsoBodyText2&quot; style=&quot;text-indent:21.0000pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0000;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;
mso-pagination:none;line-height:150%;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;font-size:10.5000pt;
mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;&quot;&gt;6&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;font-size:10.5000pt;
mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;&quot;&gt;.存在下列关联关系情形的投标人不得同时参与本项目采购(提供书面承诺)&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;font-size:10.5000pt;
mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;&quot;&gt;：&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;font-size:10.5000pt;
mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;&quot;&gt;&lt;o:p&gt;&lt;/o:p&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p class=&quot;MsoBodyText2&quot; style=&quot;text-indent:21.0000pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0000;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;
mso-pagination:none;line-height:150%;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;font-size:10.5000pt;
mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;&quot;&gt;&lt;font face=&quot;宋体&quot;&gt;（&lt;/font&gt;&lt;font face=&quot;宋体&quot;&gt;1）存在控股、管理关系&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;font-size:10.5000pt;
mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;&quot;&gt;；&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;font-size:10.5000pt;
mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;&quot;&gt;&lt;o:p&gt;&lt;/o:p&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p class=&quot;MsoBodyText2&quot; style=&quot;text-indent:21.0000pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0000;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;
mso-pagination:none;line-height:150%;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;font-size:10.5000pt;
mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;&quot;&gt;&lt;font face=&quot;宋体&quot;&gt;（&lt;/font&gt;&lt;font face=&quot;宋体&quot;&gt;2）一方直接持有另一方股权,比例超过 20%&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;font-size:10.5000pt;
mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;&quot;&gt;；&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;font-size:10.5000pt;
mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;&quot;&gt;&lt;o:p&gt;&lt;/o:p&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p class=&quot;MsoBodyText2&quot; style=&quot;text-indent:21.0000pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0000;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;
mso-pagination:none;line-height:150%;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;font-size:10.5000pt;
mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;&quot;&gt;&lt;font face=&quot;宋体&quot;&gt;（&lt;/font&gt;&lt;font face=&quot;宋体&quot;&gt;3）同时被第三方法人或非法人组织或自然人直接持有股股权,比例超过 20%(国家控股的投标人除外)&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;font-size:10.5000pt;
mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;&quot;&gt;；&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;font-size:10.5000pt;
mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;&quot;&gt;&lt;o:p&gt;&lt;/o:p&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p class=&quot;MsoBodyText2&quot; style=&quot;text-indent:21.0000pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0000;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;
mso-pagination:none;line-height:150%;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;font-size:10.5000pt;
mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;&quot;&gt;&lt;font face=&quot;宋体&quot;&gt;（&lt;/font&gt;&lt;font face=&quot;宋体&quot;&gt;4）单位负责人、董事、监事等主要人员之一为同一人(以&ldquo;国家企业信用信息公示系统&rdquo;显示的&ldquo;主要人员信息&rdquo;名单为准)。&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;font-size:10.5000pt;
mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;&quot;&gt;&lt;o:p&gt;&lt;/o:p&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p class=&quot;MsoBodyText2&quot; style=&quot;text-indent:21.0000pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0000;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;
mso-pagination:none;line-height:150%;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;font-size:10.5000pt;
mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;&quot;&gt;7.本次招标不接受分包、转包。&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;font-size:10.5000pt;
mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;&quot;&gt;&lt;o:p&gt;&lt;/o:p&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p class=&quot;MsoBodyText2&quot; style=&quot;text-indent:21.0000pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0000;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;
mso-pagination:none;line-height:150%;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;font-size:10.5000pt;
